3 Facts about how Rihanna got to where she is today:
1) After winning a beauty pageant, Rihanna caught record producer, Evan Roger's eye. She then moved to America and signed with J-Zay's record Label Def Jam.
2) She takes pride in the work she does and really enjoys what she does therefore she is very dedicated.
3) Because Rihanna had to raise her younger brothers, it taught her how to be independent, determined and strong.

Why is Rihanna inspiring to us:
She is inspiring to us because she is independent,strong and confident. She only wants to be a positive influence and she is really proud of who she is today.
